Personalysis Clustering: Homogeneity within Colors

Red (Expadite)

RED is motivated to intitiate action and stay moving. They stay focused on tasks and tangible outcomes. They have high energy, intense focus, and a sense of urgency. Cluster results below devide individuals into 3 homogeneous groups: first at a high level among all Red scores combined and then within each of the Red sub-scores for Contribution, Connection and Commitment.
